It should correctly format elseif statements at same level as if/else
{% if condition1 %}
Condition1 is truthy
{% elseif condition2 %}
Condition2 is truthy
{% else %}
Something else
{% endif %}

It should handle multiple elseif branches
{% if condition1 %}
Result 1
{% elseif condition2 %}
Result 2
{% elseif condition3 %}
Result 3
{% else %}
Default result
{% endif %}

It should handle complex conditions in elseif
{% if x > 10 %}
Large
{% elseif x > 5 and x <= 10 %}
Medium
{% elseif x > 0 %}
Small
{% else %}
Zero or negative
{% endif %}

